{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/539/comments/137654828.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo:4cbc06fc5f87..160e2f963b7b?path=src%2Frendering%2FSceneManager.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/539/_/diff#comment-137654828"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 539, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/539.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/539"}}, "title": "Forward port Selection to Citadel"}, "content": {"raw": "This is being addressed on pull request #535 (like [this](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/535/wip-align-tool-select-to-citadel/diff#Lsrc/rendering/SceneManager.ccT147)). I suggest the following be done on this pull request:\n\n* Port those `SetUserData` calls to this branch\n* Add deprecation warnings to this function\n* Substitute the `EntityFromNode` calls with `node->UserData(\"gazebo-entity\")`\n\nThen when this is merged to `Dome`, we remove this function.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>This is being addressed on <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/535/align-tool\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #535</a> (like <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/535/wip-align-tool-select-to-citadel/diff#Lsrc/rendering/SceneManager.ccT147\" rel=\"nofollow\">this</a>). I suggest the following be done on this pull request:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Port those <code>SetUserData</code> calls to this branch</li>\n<li>Add deprecation warnings to this function</li>\n<li>Substitute the <code>EntityFromNode</code> calls with <code>node-&gt;UserData(\"gazebo-entity\")</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Then when this is merged to <code>Dome</code>, we remove this function.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "cre